brainly_data.question: The spleen, liver, pancreas, and kidney are part of which body systems?
brainly_data.subject: Health

all_answers.question: The spleen, liver, pancreas, and kidney are part of which body systems?
all_answers.subject: Health
all_answers.text: Kidney is excretory. Pancreas  and liver are digestive. Spleen is lymphatic. Hope this helps. :)
